Bahaquote,is,an,invoicing,and,expensing,service,that,provides,users,with,access,to,online,invoicing,expense,monitoring,mobile,access,email,marketing,and,other,features,The,Bahaquote,platform,can,be,integrated,into,third,party,applications,and,used,for,automation,using,the,Bahaquote,API,The,API,allows,users,to,complete,transactions,online,update,billing,information,send,quotes,and,invoices,in,a,systematic,manner,through,an,automated,process,An,account,is,required,with,service